===Pronunciation===
*παιδίον / paidion / pahee-dee'-on
=== Etymology ===

*Neuter diminutive of [[παῖς]] {{GG|3816}}; a childling (of either sex), that is, (properly) an infant, or (by extension) a half grown boy or girl; figuratively an immature Christian:
===Noun===
(little, young) [[child]], [[damsel]].